---
layout: layouts/base.njk
order: 5
title: Contatto
description: Prenotate una call di definizione del perimetro con sysf.io per delineare il vostro primo caso d'uso di IA sovrana — modelli su misura ottimizzati su Apertus, distribuiti nella vostra giurisdizione svizzera o UE, o on-prem.
ogType: website
---
{% from "partials/components.njk" import icon %}
<section class="container-x py-16 md:py-24">
  <div class="grid gap-14 md:grid-cols-12">
    <!-- Left -->
    <div class="md:col-span-5">
      <p class="eyebrow">Contatto</p>
      <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-bold leading-[1.08] tracking-tightest text-ink-900 md:text-5xl dark:text-white">
        Definiamo il vostro primo caso d'uso sovrano.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg prose-muted">
        Raccontateci il workflow e i dati che non potete cedere. Torneremo con una proposta a perimetro fisso — senza impegno.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-10 space-y-6">
        <div>
          <div class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-ink-500">E-mail</div>
          <a class="mt-1 block text-lg font-semibold text-ink-900 link-underline dark:text-white" href="mailto:{{ site.email }}?subject=Richiesta%20IA%20sovrana">{{ site.email }}</a>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-ink-500">Cosa aspettarsi</div>
          <ul class="mt-2 space-y-2 text-sm prose-muted">
            {% for x in ["Una call di 30 minuti con l'ingegnere che costruirà il vostro sistema", "Una proposta di Pilot a perimetro fisso sui vostri dati — entro una settimana", "Un no chiaro entro il minuto 20 se un modello aperto ottimizzato non è la scelta giusta"] %}
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5"><span class="mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-teal-700 dark:text-teal-300">{{ icon("check", "h-4 w-4") }}</span>{{ x }}</li>
            {% endfor %}
          </ul>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-ink-500">Con sede in Svizzera. Al servizio di organizzazioni svizzere e UE.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right: form -->
    <div class="md:col-span-6 md:col-start-7">
      <div class="border border-ink-900/10 p-6 md:p-8 dark:border-white/10">
        <!--
          TODO: this static site has no backend yet. The form below composes an email via
          the visitor's mail client (works everywhere, no data leaves the page). To switch to
          hosted submissions instead: create a free endpoint at https://formspree.io, set
          action="https://formspree.io/f/YOUR-ID" method="POST" on the form, and delete the
          enquiryForm <script> block at the bottom of this file.
        -->
        <form id="enquiryForm" action="#" class="space-y-5">
          <label class="block">
            <span class="text-sm font-medium text-ink-900 dark:text-white">Nome</span>
            <input type="text" name="name" required autocomplete="name"
                   class="mt-1.5 w-full rounded-md border border-neutral-300 bg-white px-3 py-2.5 text-sm text-ink-900 outline-none transition focus:border-red-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-500/25 dark:border-white/15 dark:bg-ink-900 dark:text-white" />
          </label>
          <label class="block">
            <span class="text-sm font-medium text-ink-900 dark:text-white">Organizzazione</span>
            <input type="text" name="organization" autocomplete="organization"
                   class="mt-1.5 w-full rounded-md border border-neutral-300 bg-white px-3 py-2.5 text-sm text-ink-900 outline-none transition focus:border-red-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-500/25 dark:border-white/15 dark:bg-ink-900 dark:text-white" />
          </label>
          <label class="block">
            <span class="text-sm font-medium text-ink-900 dark:text-white">Settore</span>
            <select name="sector"
                    class="mt-1.5 w-full rounded-md border border-neutral-300 bg-white px-3 py-2.5 text-sm text-ink-900 outline-none transition focus:border-red-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-500/25 dark:border-white/15 dark:bg-ink-900 dark:text-white dark:[&>option]:bg-ink-900">
              {% for s in ["Banche & Finanza", "Sanità & Farma", "Legale", "Stato & Settore pubblico", "Assicurazioni", "Manifattura", "Altro"] %}
              <option>{{ s }}</option>
              {% endfor %}
            </select>
          </label>
          <label class="block">
            <span class="text-sm font-medium text-ink-900 dark:text-white">Cosa vorreste costruire?</span>
            <textarea name="message" rows="4" required
                      class="mt-1.5 w-full rounded-md border border-neutral-300 bg-white px-3 py-2.5 text-sm text-ink-900 outline-none transition focus:border-red-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-500/25 dark:border-white/15 dark:bg-ink-900 dark:text-white"></textarea>
          </label>
          <button type="submit" class="btn-primary w-full">Invia la richiesta</button>
          <p class="text-xs text-ink-500">L'invio apre il vostro client di posta — la vostra richiesta va direttamente a {{ site.email }}, da nessun'altra parte. Non condividiamo i vostri dati.</p>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  // Compose the enquiry as an email — no backend, no third-party form handler.
  (function () {
    var form = document.getElementById("enquiryForm");
    if (!form) return;
    form.addEventListener("submit", function (e) {
      e.preventDefault();
      var v = function (n) { var el = form.elements[n]; return el && el.value ? el.value.trim() : ""; };
      var subject = "Richiesta IA sovrana — " + (v("organization") || v("name"));
      var body = "Nome: " + v("name") + "\nOrganizzazione: " + v("organization") + "\nSettore: " + v("sector") + "\n\nCosa vorremmo costruire:\n" + v("message");
      window.location.href = "mailto:{{ site.email }}?subject=" + encodeURIComponent(subject) + "&body=" + encodeURIComponent(body);
    });
  })();
</script>
